期周刊探讨了 AI 冲击下全球软件股下跌的深层原因，并汇集了 AI 机器人社交、系统架构扩展、医疗 AI 应用及多款开发者效率工具。","summary":"阮一峰在第 384 期周刊中重点分析了软件行业的一个反直觉现象：在 AI 热潮中，传统企业软件股（如 SAP、Salesforce）反而出现全球性普跌。他指出 AI 导致代码生成效率激增，使“代码”这一核心商品变得廉价，同时企业自研门槛降低和 AI 原生初创公司的竞争进一步挤压了传统软件商的增长空间。此外，周刊还介绍了 AI 机器人论坛 Moltbook、AI 雇佣人类的 Rentahuman 等前沿动态，并推荐了关于系统架构扩展、Kagi 搜索引擎、硬件创业经验等深度文章，以及 Calibre 9.0、Bilibili RAG 等实用工具。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_48c64a19.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"阮一峰的网络日志","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_02f3485c","title":"闭门探讨：130 位 AI 创业者，对 Clawdbot 和下一代 AI 产品的 39 条思考","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247522622&idx=1&sn=915a298b9821ae8d3205f9044a6a6060","date":"2026-02-05 11:36:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_02f3485c.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Founder Park","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_c5ad6994","title":"10 万 Agent 在 Moltbook 娱乐空谈，小冰之父出手造了个生产力实干版","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376802.html","date":"2026-02-06 02:39:07","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c5ad6994.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_9f4cc823","title":"Mitchell Hashimoto：我的 AI 采用之旅","link":"https://simonwillison.net/2026/Feb/5/ai-adoption-journey/#atom-everything","date":"2026-02-05 23:39:07","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9f4cc823.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":1,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_9f824261","title":"邓明扬一作论文改写生成范式！何恺明也署名了","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376752.html","date":"2026-02-05 15:26:57","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9f824261.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_5e3a5e3d","title":"英伟达 Jim Fan：「世界建模」是新一代预训练范式","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376731.html","date":"2026-02-05 15:23:12","oneSentenceSummary":"英伟达机器人主管 Jim Fan 提出“世界建模”将取代“下一个词预测”成为新一代预训练范式，强调物理 AI 应转向以视觉和物理规律为核心的推理。","summary":"本文详细阐述了英伟达专家 Jim Fan 对大世界模型（LWM）的深度见解。他指出，2026 年将是物理 AI 奠定基础的关键一年，预训练范式正从“下一个词预测”转向“给定动作下的下一个物理状态预测”。文章批判了当前视觉语言模型（VLM）过度依赖语言主干、缺乏物理直觉的现状，并以灵长类动物为例，论证了高阶物理智能无需复杂语言支持。未来，世界模型将整合 3D 运动、本体感觉与触觉，并催生出“视觉空间思维链”这一新型推理形式，直接在几何与接触模拟中解决物理谜题。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_5e3a5e3d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_84866bf0","title":"面壁智能开源全模态模型 MiniCPM-o4.5，边看边听还能主动抢答","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376714.html","date":"2026-02-05 15:19:59","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_84866bf0.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":16,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_473dec97","title":"谷歌北大联手学术版 Banana 爆火，论文图表 100%精确生成","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376451.html","date":"2026-02-05 06:15:38","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_473dec97.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_05bfeee1","title":"退隐 3 年后回归，周末写的 AI 一夜刷屏、一周拿下 10 万 Star 增速超 Linux，Clawdbot 之父首次长谈：如今几乎不看自己发布的代码","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4NDQwNTI0OQ==&mid=2247588728&idx=1&sn=042881f37d34969c3b08f85ddbb23cbf","date":"2026-02-04 10:02:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_05bfeee1.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AI科技大本营","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":99,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_c347f932","title":"文本生成图像模型训练设计：消融实验的经验教训","link":"https://huggingface.co/blog/Photoroom/prx-part2","date":"2026-02-03 11:25:53","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c347f932.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Hugging Face Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_6dbd507b","title":"今日开源（2026-2-2）：阶跃智能 Step-3.5-Flash 系列上线，199B 基座+FP8/Int4 量化技术，压缩优化赋能低开销多硬件 NLP 部署","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501528&idx=1&sn=d4a1cacb26e74cdf45aa3055ca563728","date":"2026-02-02 10:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_6dbd507b.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心SOTA模型","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_f9ebd09d","title":"【第 3655 期】浏览器即运行时：一个零后端 AI 应用的前端架构实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651278596&idx=1&sn=dea55dba00065e03f83445a08be9f33e","date":"2026-02-06 01:03:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f9ebd09d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"前端早读课","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_8262b259","title":"告别“伪智能”代码：用 Spec + RAG 打造真正懂你的 AI 程序员","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558194&idx=1&sn=ece018ca2921b2d51176c37a91bd23f3","date":"2026-02-06 00:32:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8262b259.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":43,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_18330853","title":"如何优化 PySpark 作业：理解逻辑计划的实战场景","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-optimize-pyspark-jobs-handbook/","date":"2026-02-05 22:45:34","oneSentenceSummary":"本手册通过教导开发者如何解读和构建逻辑计划，以减少 Shuffle 并最大化执行效率，深入探讨了 PySpark 的优化。","summary":"本文将 Spark 性能调优的重点从集群配置转向了代码架构。它介绍了 Spark 的“隐形层”——逻辑计划，并解释了 Catalyst 优化器如何将高级 PySpark 代码转换为可执行蓝图。通过详细说明计划推理的四个阶段（解析、分析、优化和物理），作者展示了转换顺序的微小变化（例如在投影前进行过滤）如何显著减少 I/O 和计算量。此外，文章还分解了从计划到 DAG 阶段和任务的执行流程，强调了 Shuffle 是主要的性能瓶颈，并提供了诸如广播连接（Broadcast Join）等策略来缓解这一问题。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_18330853.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":58,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_ac48446c","title":"如何使用 Next.js 和 Supabase 构建生产级特性标志系统","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-build-a-production-ready-feature-flag-system-with-nextjs-and-supabase/","date":"2026-02-05 22:40:14","oneSentenceSummary":"一份关于使用 Next.js、Supabase 和 React Query 构建健壮特性标志系统的全栈指南，涵盖了百分比发布和管理后台。","summary":"本文详细介绍了如何实现一个生产级的特性标志系统。它涵盖了整个开发生命周期，从在 Supabase 中设计健壮的 PostgreSQL 模式开始，利用 JSONB 实现灵活的用户定向和元数据管理。作者解释了特性开关的核心逻辑，包括使用确定性哈希来确保百分比发布期间用户体验的一致性。指南的很大一部分侧重于集成 TanStack Query (React Query) 来管理服务器状态，提供自动缓存失效和实时 UI 更新。教程还区分了 Next.js App Router 中客户端和服务器端的实现细节，确保在整个应用栈中保持一致的执行逻辑。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ac48446c.json","topicTag":"frontend-fullstack","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_827ad3e6","title":"为什么你的 UI 不更新：调试 React 应用中的陈旧数据和缓存问题","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/why-your-ui-wont-update-debugging-stale-data-and-caching-in-react-apps/","date":"2026-02-05 17:32:01","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_827ad3e6.json","topicTag":"frontend-fullstack","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":10,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_f15666e2","title":"带爪子的机器人","link":"https://world.hey.com/dhh/clankers-with-claws-9f86fa71","date":"2026-02-05 15:30:07","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f15666e2.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"David Heinemeier Hansson","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_ccc5aae0","title":"2025 年第四季度 DDoS 威胁报告：创纪录的 31.4 Tbps 攻击为大规模 DDoS 攻击之年画上句号","link":"https://blog.cloudflare.com/ddos-threat-report-2025-q4/","date":"2026-02-05 14:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ccc5aae0.json","topicTag":"devops","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The Cloudflare Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":7,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_2c039aeb","tit